This page's main topic is about 'Web Design, XHTML, CSS, and JavaScript' and is composed of ???<br /><br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>&lt;body&gt;<br /> &lt;h1&gt;Web Design&lt;/h1&gt;<br />  &lt;section&gt;<br />   &lt;h1&gt;XHTML&lt;/h1&gt;<br /> &lt;/section&gt;<br /><br />  &lt;section&gt;<br />   &lt;h1&gt;CSS&lt;/h1&gt;<br /> &lt;/section&gt;<br /><br />  &lt;section&gt;<br />   &lt;h1&gt;JavaScript&lt;/h1&gt;<br /> &lt;/section&gt;<br />&lt;/body&gt;</code></dd></dl><br /><br />This page is about 'Web Design' which is composed of 'XHTML', 'CSS', and 'JavaScript'.<br /><br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>&lt;body&gt;<br /> &lt;h1&gt;Web Design&lt;/h1&gt;<br />  &lt;section&gt;<br />   &lt;h2&gt;XHTML&lt;/h2&gt;<br /> &lt;/section&gt;<br /><br />  &lt;section&gt;<br />   &lt;h2&gt;CSS&lt;/h2&gt;<br /> &lt;/section&gt;<br /><br />  &lt;section&gt;<br />   &lt;h2&gt;JavaScript&lt;/h2&gt;<br /> &lt;/section&gt;<br />&lt;/body&gt;</code></dd></dl><br /><br />By allowing h1 to exist multiple times we could say, &quot;&lt;h1&gt;XHTML&lt;/h1&gt; is &lt;h1&gt;XML&lt;/h1&gt; and &lt;h1&gt;XML&lt;/h1&gt; is &lt;h1&gt;XHTML&lt;/h1&gt;&quot; which is false.<br /><br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>&lt;body&gt;<br /> &lt;h1&gt;XML&lt;/h1&gt;<br />  &lt;section&gt;<br />   &lt;h1&gt;XHTML&lt;/h1&gt;<br /> &lt;/section&gt;<br />&lt;/body&gt;</code></dd></dl><br /><br />By forcing the h1 element to legally exist only once then we could say &quot;&lt;h2&gt;XHTML&lt;/h2&gt; is a subset of &lt;h1&gt;XML&lt;/h1&gt;&quot; which is true.<br /><br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>&lt;body&gt;<br /> &lt;h1&gt;XML&lt;/h1&gt;<br />  &lt;section&gt;<br />   &lt;h2&gt;XHTML&lt;/h2&gt;<br /> &lt;/section&gt;<br />&lt;/body&gt;</code></dd></dl><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=47">JAB Creations</a> — Tue Mar 02, 2010 7:53 pm</p><hr />
